<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>zài nǐ de shēn biān yǒu yī zuò qí dǎo shān 迦南1112</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zài nǐ de shēn biān yǒu yī zuò qí dǎo shān, shān lù wān wān zhí dào shān diān.
 shén zài nà lǐ yǔ nǐ yǒu yuē, zài shān dǐng shén yào yǔ nǐ huì miàn.
 nǐ jiāng huì kàn jiàn cóng mò kàn jiàn de, wú shù zuò qí dǎo de shān fēng jǐn jǐn xiāng lián.
 xiāng qì màn màn wéi rào qí dǎo shān, xīng xīng zhī huǒ yǐ jīng liáo yuán.
 qí dǎo de huǒ yàn dài lái xuān jiào de huǒ yàn, xuān jiào de huǒ yàn dài lái fù xìng de huǒ yàn,
 fù xìng de huǒ yàn yǐ zài quán de diǎn rán. yīn wèi nǐ měi tiān dōu pān dēng gāo gāo de qí dǎo shān.
 yīn wèi nǐ měi tiān dōu pān dēng gāo gāo de qí dǎo shān.</lyrics>
</song>